{"tid":977795,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"異國戀嘅困惑","createTime":"2019-01-11T12:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T13:38:12.000Z","uid":151405,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd783e6d731a638a147cc79eebcf290691b60c8","tid":977795,"uid":151405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"今日同男朋友拍咗拖啱啱好一年<br />\n係因為我一個人去旅行而識嘅<br />\n我地相方係自己嘅城市都有自己嘅工作同學業<br />\n<br />\n一開始嘅時候無諗太多 覺得有feel就一齊<br />\n還掂都係青春 反正今日又唔知聽日事<br />\n所以就一齊 慢慢走到一年<br />\n<br />\n呢一年裡面 我地每晚都會facetime<br />\n每日都可以keep住gdmorning / gdnite<br />\n生活嘅大小事我地都會知道<br />\nCulture conflict 都已經過咗<br />\n了解對方一切事情<br />\n<br />\n依家大概平均每個月飛一次<br />\n搭飛機搭到好似搭巴士咁<br />\n然後每一次見都仲係好有feel<br />\n會成日好掛住對方<br />\n<br />\n其實我master grad 有諗過去佢個邊搵工<br />\n但係奈何我唔係嗰邊嘅專業人才<br />\n去到個邊會失業 而香港就可以40k<br />\n至於佢 都係自己嘅國家發展比較合適<br />\n前途亦都比較好<br />\n<br />\n我其實好想同佢講<br />\n我愛佢 我都可以為佢放棄一切<br />\n但咁樣做會唔會太傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多幾年就三十歲<br />\n我覺得男朋友其實都知呢個問題<br />\n但佢都從來冇講過甚至提過<br />\n究竟係我驚 定係其實佢都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好驚講咗出黎會迫住大家要面對<br />\n我唔想相愛嘅兩個人因為現實而放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n上一段愛情長跑九年被分手<br />\n我每一次都好努力付出<br />\n其實對愛情都幾失望<br />\n如果愛情一直無結果<br />\n我應該會選擇以後都一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb029b51f808a66b87a77171350a4d794aa2e2","tid":977795,"uid":22756,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"Gay佬f小陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028ad91694b615b53d784d5f96bc4f9eb51f5703","tid":977795,"uid":151405,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dbdb029b51f808a66b87a77171350a4d794aa2e2","tid":977795,"uid":22756,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"Gay佬f小陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:49:57.000Z","msg":"連登唔係淨係得男人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2964859f8c8233d4703d88062908a79ca64c5a41","tid":977795,"uid":200394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902c6d914bf40221e4cfcdf72646d36d50156bb4","tid":977795,"uid":151405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2964859f8c8233d4703d88062908a79ca64c5a41","tid":977795,"uid":200394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"但去咗一定年紀 迫你一定要諗呢啲<br />\n而且愛對方先會想同對方行落去"},{"pid":"df22d4de4abfc917af37e45efade6eaf2706ca3e","tid":977795,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"同佢講，試下搵工先，遲早都要面對，或者揀間公司留一兩年後可以外派去佢個度做"}]}